705743f-a.title: Brooklyn: Moffat Street - Wilson Avenue
705743f-a.text:
Moffat Street, west side, between Wilson and Knickerbocker Aves.
The brick building to the right of the frame house, is No. 253.
January 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
